<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Connexion TikTok Réussie - Only Matt</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #000;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .success-card {
            background: #111;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .icon-circle {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: #25F4EE; /* TikTok Cyan */
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            font-size: 40px;
            color: #000;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(37, 244, 238, 0.4);
        }
        h1 { margin: 0 0 15px; font-weight: 700; background: linear-gradient(45deg, #25F4EE, #FE2C55); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;}
        p { color: #888; line-height: 1.6; }
        .code-box {
            background: #222;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: left;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: monospace;
            overflow-x: auto;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            color: #ddd;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #dddddd;
            color: #000;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn:hover { background: #fff; transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .logo { font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin-top: 30px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="success-card">
        <div class="icon-circle">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-tiktok"></i>
        </div>
        <h1>Connexion Réussie !</h1>
        <p>Votre compte TikTok a été connecté avec succès à l'application Spread It.</p>

        <% if (tokenData) { %>
            <div class="code-box">
                <div><strong>TIKTOK_ACCESS_TOKEN=</strong><%= tokenData.access_token %></div>
                <div style="margin-top:10px;"><strong>TIKTOK_REFRESH_TOKEN=</strong><%= tokenData.refresh_token %></div>
                <div style="margin-top:10px;"><strong>TIKTOK_OPEN_ID=</strong><%= tokenData.open_id %></div>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9em;">Copiez ces clés dans votre configuration si nécessaire.</p>
        <% } %>

        <a href="/composer" class="btn">Retourner au Dashboard</a>
        
        <div class="logo">Powered by Only Matt</div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
